data.title: William Davis, Jr. - Homicide Victim
data.meta_description: On Saturday June 25, 2005 at approximately 6:15 am, William “Billy” Davis, Jr. was shot to death in the 2300 block of Pitts Place, SE. The Metropolitan Police Department seeks the public’s assistance in gathering information regarding this incident.
